    • Field Detail

      • includeActivities

        protected boolean includeActivities
        If true, Activitys will be processed.

      • includeActivityProjects

        protected boolean includeActivityProjects
        If true, ActivityProjects will be processed.

      • includeTranslations

        protected boolean includeTranslations
        If true, the export file contains TranslateTerms.

      • includePhysicalRemovements

        protected boolean includePhysicalRemovements
        If true, PhysDel will be processed.

      • includeUsers

        protected boolean includeUsers
        If true, UserInfos will be processed.

      • includeReplicationSets

        protected boolean includeReplicationSets
        If true, ReplSetNames will be processed. To get an export file to synchronize the replication sets between sites set this value to true and includeSords to false.

      • includeSords

        protected boolean includeSords
        If true, Sords will be processed.

      • targets

        protected java.util.List<ReplSetName> targets
        Optional list of specific targets. If this list is not null and not empty, export the whole archive information that belongs to the specified target sites. This also includes documents that were replicated to that target already.

      • compressionLevel

        protected int compressionLevel
        Enables compression mode. -1=no compression, 0/1=low compression, 9=strong compression.

      • timeStampStart

        protected java.lang.String timeStampStart
        This value applies to exports only. Objects modified before this timestamp will not be processed.

      • timeStampEnd

        protected java.lang.String timeStampEnd
        This value applies to exports only. Objects modified after this timestamp will not be processed.
